                    | . Columns are always contained within a row.
                    strong Rows are indicated by a dashed grey line and rounded corners
                    | .
            hr
            .row
                .text-center.col-md-12
                    .well
                        strong  Easily build your page using the Bootstrap components from the Insert panel.
            .row
                .col-sm-4.text-center
                    h4
                        | Adding
                        strong Buttons
                    p
                        | Quickly add buttons to your page by using the button component in the insert panel.
                    button.btn.btn-info.btn-sm(type='button') Info Button
                    button.btn.btn-success.btn-sm(type='button') Success Button
                .text-center.col-sm-4
                    h4
                        | Adding
                        strong Labels
                    p Using the insert panel, add labels to your page by using the label component.
                    span.label.label-warning Info Label
                    span.label.label-danger Danger Label
                .text-center.col-sm-4
                    h4
